Undergraduate Student LoansCover up to 100% of your school-certified college costs with our zero fee undergraduate loans.call-us onApply Now





APPLY NOWor

callCall us at 18007883368 1-800-STUDENT








Loans for Undergraduate StudentsOur zero fee private student loans for students seeking undergraduate degrees complement federal student loans and other financial aid to help you pay for college. Applying online is quick and easy and our knowledgeable Student Loan Specialists are ready to help you 24/7.


Variable Interest Rates

 APR -  APR
(3-Month LIBOR +  to 3-Month LIBOR + )


Fixed Interest Rates

 APR -  APR


View APR Examples
				  APRs reflect interest rates as of 








ZERO FEESNo loan application fees. No origination fees. No late fees.



				REWARDS
Rewards for Good Grades
Get a one-time 1% cash reward  on each new Discover student loan when you get at least a 3.0 GPA (or equivalent).
more 


Auto Debit Reward
Get a 0.25% interest rate reduction when you are enrolled in automatic payments during repayment.
more  



