Our Commitment To Your Donations

At DonationTo.com our number 1 goal is to ensure your cause or charity keeps 100% of donations collected. We are a leading provider of an online fundraising tool. Today we are revolutionizing how people connect with and give to charities online and, unlike other platforms, pass 100% of what you give, or raise to charities without taking a percentage and avoiding credit card fees. Charities and causes lose over an estimated $750 million a year in fees. By using DonationTo to crowdfund and raise money online your donations raised go directly to you and your cause. 

